1.0.name: wordpress/seocare
1.0.description: SeoCare helps the admin to create SEO-Friendly posts. It has several rules that can be edited in the options. After creating the post SeoCare calculates a grade for the post. That way you can easely see on what points you better can change your article so it would score better on SEO.
